<p>Sets the left, right or center alignment of the text block.</p>


<pre class="language-csharp"><code class="language-csharp">public TextAlignment Alignment { get; set; }</code></pre>

<h2 id="remarks">Remarks</h2><p>Set this property to <a href="./../ref/Topten.RichTextKit.TextAlignment#Topten.RichTextKit-TextAlignment-Auto">TextAlignment.Auto</a> to align
the paragraph according to the <a href="./../ref/Topten.RichTextKit.TextBlock.BaseDirection">BaseDirection</a>.</p>
<ul>
<li>If the <a href="./../ref/Topten.RichTextKit.TextBlock.MaxWidth">MaxWidth</a> property has been set this will
be used for alignment calculations.</li>
<li>If the <a href="./../ref/Topten.RichTextKit.TextBlock.MaxWidth">MaxWidth</a> property has not been set, the
width of the longest line will be used.</li>
</ul>

